parameters:
\n<Cleaning Robot>"Those who don't sort their trash, who don't dispose of it
in the designated areas, are the real trash of this city."

\n<Cleaning Robot>This is a recording from Lady Marion. It will play
automatically when someone approaches.
\n<Cleaning Robot>You're Eury-san, right? Please take this.

\n<Cleaning Robot>"When you're busy, it's okay to start with any task. In
fact, it's better to wait until you're mentally settled
down."

\n<Cleaning Robot>"This is a recording data for Lady Marion. It will
automatically play when the memory usage exceeds 99%."
\n<Cleaning Robot>"This is for you, Eury-san. Please take this."

\n<Cleaning Robot>By moving side to side like this, I'm giving off the
impression that I'm doing something.
\n<Cleaning Robot>You're Eury-san, right? Please take this.

\n<Sexaroid>...Ufufu. I can't help but grin, even though I'm not saying
anything naughty.

\n<Worker>I see, it's about time to start working. Hmm, I'll roll
around a bit more and then I'll get to it.
\n<Suspicious person>...What are you looking at?! Get lost!
\n<Eury>You're the one who stole the materials, aren't you?!!

\n<Eury>It looks like she went towards the \C[2]exit of Tengen
Street\C[0]. Let's chase after her!

\n<Patrol Robot>Looking at plants somehow makes you feel at ease, doesn't
it?

\n<Patrol Robot>...I wondered if everyone would like this kind of "robots
and plants" combination, so I decided to try it out.
\n<Patrol Robot>You're Eury-san, right? Please take this.
